title: Nomad Factory Complete Bundle
description:
All Nomad Factory software in one pack! Contains everything released to date.

This includes:

The complete Analog Signature series:

- Limiting Amplifier LM-662 v1.3
- Program Equalizer EQP-4 v1.3
- Studio Channel SC-226 v1.3

The complete Blue Tubes series:

- Blue Tubes Analog Trackbox v1.3
- Blue Tubes Dynamics Pack v3.2
- Blue Tubes Effects Pack v3.2
- Blue Tubes Equalizers Pack v3.2

Other bundles:

- Analog Mastering Tools v1.0
- Essential Studio Suite v1.5
- Liquid Bundle v1.6
- Liquid Bundle II v2.4
- Retrology M-Tone EQ v1.0
- Free Bundle

Other commercial plugins:

- BBE D82 Sonic Maximizer v2.0
- BlueVerb DRV-2080 v1.4
- Rock Amp Legends v1.5

Other free plugins:

- TubeScreamer



NOTE:

The TubeScreamer plugin was developed for the french "Recording Musicien" magazine. This plugin isn&#039;t mentioned on Nomad Factory&#039;s official website.
